01:11:41.500 --> 01:11:43.500
Or should he agree

01:11:43.500 --> 01:11:45.500
with his boss every step?

01:11:45.500 --> 01:11:47.500
Or is his every step prescribed

01:11:47.500 --> 01:11:49.500
and described in the system

01:11:49.500 --> 01:11:51.500
of duties?

01:11:51.500 --> 01:11:53.500
The second is the influence of activity

01:11:53.500 --> 01:11:55.500
on the end result.

01:11:55.500 --> 01:11:57.500
There are jobs that are not very important

01:11:57.500 --> 01:11:59.500
for the company's end result,

01:11:59.500 --> 01:12:01.500
