And also the scope of control.

01:12:13.500 --> 01:12:15.500
This is the field of control

01:12:15.500 --> 01:12:17.500
over people, actions, situations,

01:12:17.500 --> 01:12:19.500
and results that are provided

01:12:19.500 --> 01:12:21.500
for this position.

